" EXPORTING TO HTML... (see ':he 2html')

"   Edit another file in the same directory as the current file
"   uses expression to extract path from current file's path
"  (thanks Douglas Potts)
if has("unix")
    map ,e :e <C-R>=expand("%:p:h") . "/" <CR>
else
    map ,e :e <C-R>=expand("%:p:h") . "\" <CR>
endif

